{
  "texts": [
    "For better sustainability, reducing operational energy usage and energy wastage alone is not sufficient.",
    "Using green energy as much as possible and minimizing power supply to the infrastructure is equally crucial.",
    "To attain this goal, the implementation of a demand response program [130] has become indispensable.",
    "It provides a balance between demand and supply in the Cloud-Edge Continuum by efficiently coordinating with available energy sources.",
    "This strategy employs direct and indirect load control strategy to optimize power usage and maintain a balance between the demand and supply of electricity [62]."
  ]
}